Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.70,0:03:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能发送D-MAIL吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.58,0:03:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确说得通
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.16,0:03:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么大声
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.00,0:03:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喊得我头疼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.91,0:03:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.08,0:03:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr.显像管这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.29,0:03:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到会暴力相向…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.46,0:03:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这就是活该
