Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.07,0:05:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 如果只是读取存储在颞叶里的记忆信号的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.91,0:05:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想应该都能在秋叶原找到…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.45,0:05:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.53,0:05:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯? 怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.24,0:05:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是电话烤箱很有可能不足以压缩人类的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.75,0:05:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.92,0:05:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.80,0:05:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.67,0:05:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 我现在就写一下需要的零件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.10,0:05:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些东西太难了 真由喜一头雾水啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.26,0:05:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才克里斯蒂娜不也说了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.60,0:05:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让自己此刻的意识跳回到过去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.06,0:06:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得有点可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.23,0:06:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有D-MAIL还不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.20,0:06:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D-MAIL的不确定因素太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.07,0:06:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只凭一封邮件 就会引发无法预料的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.87,0:06:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让记忆回到过去就没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.66,0:06:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少就改变过去而言 这样可以在某种程度上进行控制
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.21,0:06:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像改变整个秋叶原这样的变化就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.63,0:06:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整个秋叶原?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.43,0:06:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.55,0:06:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 把记忆发送到过去之后 现在的自己会怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.64,0:06:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体还是会留在这里的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.42,0:06:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.51,0:06:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 现在真由喜是跟你说着话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.40,0:06:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这个真由喜跳跃回一星期前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.55,0:06:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会重新经历这一星期 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.36,0:06:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那个时候没有和你交谈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.57,0:06:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那会变成怎样呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.95,0:07:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…你可能会留有谈过话的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.99,0:07:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而进行过谈话的事实却会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.29,0:07:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 真由喜虽然记得跟你谈过话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.29,0:07:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你却完全不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.92,0:07:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.55,0:07:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真是这样 会很寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.89,0:07:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.51,0:07:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.68,0:07:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真由喜…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.02,0:07:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是萌郁小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.56,0:07:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌郁小姐～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.03,0:07:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘟嘟噜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.12,0:07:50.25,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(819,660)}shining finger
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.12,0:07:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸色还真是阴沉啊 闪光的指压师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.55,0:07:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间机器报废了?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.72,0:08:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在用哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.47,0:08:03.81,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(848,660)}time leap
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.47,0:08:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且啊  这回没准能进行时间跳跃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.81,0:08:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别随便讲出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.81,0:08:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌郁小姐不也是LabMem吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.94,0:08:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.51,0:08:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz6\fs18\bord0\pos(677,194)}那是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.51,0:08:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\frz6\fs18\bord0\pos(523,314)}时间跳跃是什么?\N请详细告诉我\N萌郁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.11,0:08:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间跳跃是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.44,0:08:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是字面上的意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.94,0:08:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让记忆跳跃时空
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.74,0:08:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记忆…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.45,0:08:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌郁小姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.08,0:08:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌郁小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.21,0:08:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.26,0:08:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先在秋叶原转悠比较有效率吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.68,0:08:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.02,0:08:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是绹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.69,0:08:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.02,0:08:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.65,0:08:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是这副打扮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.65,0:08:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 店长怒吼说「给我一天都保持这样子!」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.57,0:09:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于好孩子来说你这身打扮有点伤眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.45,0:09:06.45,neta1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(15,20,15,10,0,200)\pos(15,10)\fad(300, 300)}眼の毒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.15,0:09:06.66,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx0\pos(15,20)\t(0,200,1,\fscx100)\t(5300,0,1,\fscx0)}———
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.45,0:09:06.45,neta3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(15,20,15,50,0,200)\pos(15,50)\fad(300, 300)}既有看了会伤眼的意思，也有看了会想要的意思。\N此处铃羽按照字面理解成了有毒的东西。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.66,0:09:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毒? 我特地没带有毒的东西出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.03,0:09:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.04,0:09:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 其实是绹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.29,0:09:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她好像有话想对你说 到处找你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.04,0:09:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我说?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.92,0:09:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 刚才爸爸做了很过分的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.17,0:09:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绹…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.47,0:09:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了说这个而特意…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.68,0:09:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何等懂礼貌的小动物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.05,0:09:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是小动物啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.22,0:09:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心 我平时也总是给Mr.显像管添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.69,0:09:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是扯平了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.27,0:09:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不像你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.90,0:09:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎? 他平时就是这样的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.03,0:09:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真由喜差不多要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.16,0:09:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有约吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.12,0:09:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 Cosplayer吹雪酱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.45,0:09:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去给她送COS服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.83,0:09:55.84,neta1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(15,20,15,10,0,200)\pos(15,10)\fad(300, 300)}CM
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.54,0:09:56.04,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx0\pos(15,20)\t(0,200,1,\fscx100)\t(5300,0,1,\fscx0)}———
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.83,0:09:55.84,neta3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(15,20,15,50,0,200)\pos(15,50)\fad(300, 300)}Comic Market的简写，\N是由Comic Market准备会举办的日本以至全球最大型的同人志即卖会。\N略称Comiket或 CM。现时每年八月的第二个星期五至日和十二月二十九\N及三十日均在位于东京都台场的东京国际展示场举行，免费入场。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.04,0:09:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说起来 差不多是CM了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.17,0:09:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 再见哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.67,0:09:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铃小姐和绹也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.46,0:09:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘟嘟噜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.84,0:09:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.92,0:10:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们也回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.09,0:10:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我还得去找克里斯蒂娜要我买的零件
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.43,0:10:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牧瀬红莉栖…她和SERN是一伙的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.41,0:10:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SERN的间谍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.28,0:10:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.29,0:10:38.30,neta1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(15,20,15,10,0,200)\pos(15,10)\fad(300, 300)}ぬるぽ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.00,0:10:38.50,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx0\pos(15,20)\t(0,200,1,\fscx100)\t(5300,0,1,\fscx0)}———
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.29,0:10:38.30,neta3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(15,20,15,50,0,200)\pos(15,50)\fad(300, 300)}@ch用语。\NJAVA程序语言中的异常，即NullPointerException。\N最初起源于@ch的程序员版的一个“让我们管NullPointerException叫ぬるぽ吧”的帖子。\N以后每当出现这个词，都会惯例有人用“ガッ（GA）”来回应。“ガッ”表示殴打，起源的\N一种说法是在goo词典里搜索“ぬるぽ”会得到殴打的解释。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.50,0:10:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NULLPO
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.25,0:10:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GA!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.84,0:10:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无声无息地靠近是犯规的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.76,0:10:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是在@ch上发帖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.59,0:10:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…这才不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.05,0:10:48.64,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老早就发现你是根正苗红的@cher了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.60,0:10:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.43,0:10:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今再想隐瞒什么意义都没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.94,0:10:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郁闷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.23,0:10:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.15,0:10:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后就正式授予克里斯蒂娜@cher的称号
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.44,0:11:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再给我取奇怪的外号了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.86,0:11:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 你要给我保密啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.95,0:11:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.32,0:11:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光明正大地写进简历不是挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.95,0:11:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兴趣是@ch
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.74,0:11:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果学者是@cher的话 肯定能盖一两个帖子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.96,0:11:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盖那个干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.21,0:11:18.21,neta1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(15,20,15,10,0,200)\pos(15,10)\fad(300, 300)}anchor
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.92,0:11:18.42,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx0\pos(15,20)\t(0,200,1,\fscx100)\t(5300,0,1,\fscx0)}———
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.21,0:11:18.21,neta3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(15,20,15,50,0,200)\pos(15,50)\fad(300, 300)}@ch上一般写作“安価”，意为锚点，指在bbs上指定发言序号进行发帖（回帖）。\N在@ch上一般是使用『＞＞数字』的形式。此后衍生出了“锚点游戏”这样的玩法。\N这种游戏的玩法是先提前指定２０～３０个数字之后的序号，然后当那个序号的帖子出现后，\N指定的人就要按照那个帖子上写的内容去做，是一种在ＶＩＰ区很流行的玩法。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.42,0:11:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还是说在VIP区玩Anchor更好些?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.88,0:11:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真恨这个听得懂含义的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.30,0:11:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.22,0:11:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此不善于伪装自己的人要是间谍…实在无法想象
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.43,0:11:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊? 你在说什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.47,0:11:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 打工战士说你是SERN的间谍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.98,0:11:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么 找碴吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.69,0:11:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.48,0:11:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全同意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.61,0:11:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你虽然是机关派来的间谍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.99,0:11:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却改变了心意 心甘情愿地当了我的助手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.58,0:11:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也不对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.62,0:11:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是 项目进行得怎么样了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.54,0:11:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,项目?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.67,0:11:54.92,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(620,660)}time leap
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.67,0:11:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间跳跃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.96,0:11:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零件我可是都买回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.71,0:12:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对哦 是该开始做了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.84,0:12:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都到这一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.80,0:12:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.89,0:12:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.22,0:12:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是一方面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.10,0:12:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的做出来了会怎样…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.27,0:12:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我其实是想说…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.81,0:12:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.02,0:12:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是告诉你吧 反正我都已经暴露大半了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.61,0:12:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这里不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.45,0:12:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得在看不见你的地方才行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.33,0:12:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…和父亲之间有些问题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.38,0:12:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 在阿肯色州被落雷击中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.21,0:12:43.43,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(837,660)}dark side
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.21,0:12:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯蒂娜的父亲便陷入了黑暗面之中…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.43,0:12:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想开玩笑的话 我就不说了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.43,0:12:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 你说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.35,0:12:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简单来说 我被父亲讨厌了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.98,0:12:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…是憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.94,0:12:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不是作为女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.36,0:12:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是作为一个科学家 一个对手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.07,0:13:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的父亲曾是个物理学家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.24,0:13:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从小就很喜欢听父亲讲那些复杂的物理知识
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.37,0:13:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得益于此 小学五六年级时我就已经能理解父亲的论文了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.29,0:13:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我就开始自己写论文 也得了不少奖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.43,0:13:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但得不得奖其实根本无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.85,0:13:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是觉得和父亲讨论问题很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.93,0:13:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过邮件交换了很多论文 加深讨论
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.81,0:13:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不知从何时开始父亲不再回信了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.57,0:13:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在享受讨论的时候 我也驳倒了他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.58,0:13:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指出父亲的错误
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.91,0:13:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不知不觉中…伤害了他的自尊心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.09,0:13:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲和母亲疏远了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.68,0:14:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了自信 紧接着又被学术界排斥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.39,0:14:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后一次见面时 父亲对我说了这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.19,0:14:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在可怜我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.23,0:14:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在蔑视我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.15,0:14:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就凭你个当女儿的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.99,0:14:26.58,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(794,660)}time leap
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.99,0:14:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我制造出了能进行时间跳跃的装置
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.04,0:14:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲肯定会气疯掉的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.13,0:14:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比之前更加生气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.50,0:14:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才犹豫着做不做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.30,0:14:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是无须担心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.88,0:14:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正最后肯定会做的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.22,0:14:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你说的 我最喜欢做实验了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果发现了什么 就一定会想要去确认
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.44,0:14:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像曾经的父亲一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.90,0:14:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像父亲和我一起生活时那样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.96,0:15:10.13,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(756,660)}Operation Verthandi
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.96,0:15:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 马上就开始 掌管现在的女神 计划
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.34,0:15:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间磨蹭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.05,0:15:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为机关马上就要攻打这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.05,0:15:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果还是这个?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.59,0:15:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.93,0:15:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是凤凰院凶真
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.64,0:15:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背负着改变世界构造的使命!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.73,0:15:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道就不对你说了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.40,0:15:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于此同时 也得让你们和解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.77,0:15:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父亲现在在哪?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.44,0:15:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎? 在青森…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去的话 资金也是问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.41,0:15:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果决定时间了 就尽早告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.70,0:15:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难…难道你想和我一起去?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.37,0:15:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.71,0:15:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了达成我的野心 你必须得在最好的精神状态下工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.46,0:15:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我凤凰院凶真陪你一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后察言观色并巧妙地提供话题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.39,0:15:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回收你与父亲之间的芥蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.30,0:15:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.93,0:16:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是自称科学狂人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.89,0:16:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会察言观色呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.35,0:16:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.32,0:16:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.99,0:16:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有时人还挺好的 真让人纠结
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.66,0:16:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果明白了我的伟大之处 就赶快回去工作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.95,0:16:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.00,0:16:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说在前面 既然已经决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.33,0:16:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算生拉硬扯我也会带你去的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.84,0:16:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求之不得
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.26,0:16:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘟…嘟…噜……
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.52,0:16:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 真由理酱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.69,0:16:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了? 拿这么多东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.24,0:16:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是把那个什么冈伦叫来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.87,0:16:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.44,0:16:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.63,0:16:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看这里啊 不是明明写着「牧瀬」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.34,0:16:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道不是叫牧瀬布丁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.72,0:16:58.72,neta1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(15,20,15,10,0,200)\pos(15,10)\fad(300, 300)}森永和小岩井
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.42,0:16:58.89,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx0\pos(15,20)\t(0,200,1,\fscx100)\t(5300,0,1,\fscx0)}————
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.72,0:16:58.72,neta3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(15,20,15,50,0,200)\pos(15,50)\fad(300, 300)}两家都是日本有名的乳业公司。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.92,0:16:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟森永布丁和小岩井布丁一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.05,0:16:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别强词夺理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.39,0:17:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说 牧瀬是什么东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.01,0:17:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的名字!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.43,0:17:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯蒂娜·牧瀬吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.35,0:17:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你老老实实地写上克里斯蒂娜的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.10,0:17:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不会不小心摄入多余的卡路里了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.11,0:17:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅自吃了别人的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.86,0:17:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说了 那个是我的勺子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.90,0:17:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要随便用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.20,0:17:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还不是随便使用了Lab的宝库吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.28,0:17:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到达
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.95,0:17:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了? 那些是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.00,0:17:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,COS服的材料和真由喜的过夜行李啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.63,0:17:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过夜?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.25,0:17:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我要做CM上用的COS服
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.80,0:17:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.97,0:17:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母同意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.09,0:17:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经好好说过了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.85,0:17:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯酱也会留下来过夜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.76,0:17:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了改良电话烤箱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.18,0:17:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧…我也想过是不是要留下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.39,0:17:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是在这里过夜会很郁闷的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.90,0:17:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为凤凰院什么先生会擅自吃掉别人的布丁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.32,0:17:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是凤凰院凶真!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.90,0:17:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字至少给我记住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.28,0:17:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没资格说我!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.66,0:17:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说布丁这事你就无视了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.78,0:18:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能还是回去比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.00,0:18:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是可以留下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.00,0:18:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话让冈部出去比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.00,0:18:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.33,0:18:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于我来说 Lab就是灵魂的归处
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.09,0:18:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然让我出去?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.63,0:18:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么一起留宿的条件是出来买东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.18,0:18:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细想想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.30,0:18:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像从昨天开始就一直被助手呼来唤去的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.56,0:18:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯蒂娜吗
