Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.40,0:18:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼…你兴奋个什么劲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.44,0:18:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要忘记你作为LabMem的本职工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.78,0:18:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没兴奋呢 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.95,0:18:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎?什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.66,0:18:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么啦 快点进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.29,0:18:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁冈部回来之前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.30,0:18:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是助手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:19:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz15\fs34\bord0\be1\pos(512,515)}你知道的太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.24,0:19:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs110\bord0\be5\move(401,608,140,608)}你知道的太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.44,0:19:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.58,0:19:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.01,0:19:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.22,0:19:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.22,0:20:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.22,0:20:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原谅!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.56,0:20:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不可原谅!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.52,0:20:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈伦 真由喜十分伤心 也很害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.61,0:20:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 不仅偷窥浴室还把要买的东西都丢下了?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.36,0:20:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.12,0:20:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说冈部
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.24,0:20:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈伦?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.25,0:20:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 桶子君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.33,0:20:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了? 大半夜的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.00,0:20:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.89,0:20:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在外面用电脑连接了一下 觉得有点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.00,0:20:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.23,0:21:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在这里跟SERN中枢的线路是直接连接着的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.23,0:21:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SERN?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.27,0:21:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说已经掌握整个系统了?
